NGR Soldier
The New German Republic Soldier is a frontline combatant of one of Europe's
most powerful human nations. The NGR fights a constant war against Brodkil
demons and Gargoyle invaders, and its soldiers are trained for that specific
and brutal conflict. NGR Soldiers are disciplined, well-equipped, and fight
for a nation that actually has a chance of survival.

NGR Soldiers choose from Weapons, Physical, Military, and Technical skill
categories. They are trained in energy weapons, tactics, radio communications,
and basic field medicine.

Attribute requirements: PS 10, PE 10.
Starting equipment: NGR infantry body armor, NGR assault rail gun, personal
radio, combat knife, and standard field kit.
